title: TaNi$_{2}$Te$_{2}$ Structure
comments:
We use the data in ICSD Entry 66346, which references the German language version of (Tremel, 1992). 
 \href{current_web_home_dir/A2BC2_oP20_62_2c_c_2c-001}{TaNi$_{2}$Te$_{2}$} and \href{current_web_home_dir/A2BC2_oP20_62_2c_c_2c-002}{NaCu$_{2}$O$_{2}$} have the same AFLOW prototype label, A2BC2\_oP20\_62\_2c\_c\_2c. They are generated by the same symmetry operations with different sets of parameters ({\tt -{-}params}) specified in their corresponding CIF files.
